				This spell is a GREAT one to get.  Although it takes a lot of mana, it is well worth it.  It will make you better in a group, to fill the role of the pure caster.  In the Prima Guidebook, it says this spell does 33 + 1/lvl.  I have to disagree with that, it seemed to me that it did around 41. I used this spell until lvl 15. It's that good.  At lvl 15, it did 47 (which is the max.)  I advise you, buy this spell asap... it helps a lot!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<BR>
